{"tid":1044223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖又煩 單身又煩 做人真係好慘","createTime":"2019-03-02T17:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T03:50:16.000Z","uid":92866,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"af582056ec4812fbb4f4d3e7507442a800fedeba","tid":1044223,"uid":92866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只想要多啲時間<br />\n做我想做既野<br />\n<br />\n鍾意人 拍緊拖既話 又要追又要溝 仲要估嚟估去<br />\n<br />\n同異性做朋友 又驚我或者佢諗多左<br />\n<br />\n同有伴既講多兩句 又要怕佢另一伴唔鍾意<br />\n<br />\n單身又好似有罪咁<br />\n係咪你：肥/醜/高要求/港女格/圈子細...<br />\n好鬼煩<br />\n不如去識多啲野 學下新野仲好過<br />\n搞唔掂咁多人際關係<br />\n果然人類既所有煩惱都係來自人際關係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974c0750030086728a54c96a46164c1c3e7e5023","tid":1044223,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"所以訓吧啦"},{"pid":"ee391d172b48e4b77431d9a2c7d1c76ef1f5740d","tid":1044223,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"拍拖邊煩"},{"pid":"2bbd821d3f6a32fdc1b05a61e5ab4da31c48c6ce","tid":1044223,"uid":212143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"又呢又路 阿芝阿左<br />\n訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84eb6014f5d517507eab68bd756230f356420b4a","tid":1044223,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee391d172b48e4b77431d9a2c7d1c76ef1f5740d","tid":1044223,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"拍拖邊煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5909542470b5684f58b22c2fba71bf430d58425","tid":1044223,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite